para.span: 如果所请求的类型的默认文件夹不存在，具体取决于类型，Outlook 可能会创建并返回该文件夹，或可能会引发错误。

span.span: If the default folder of the requested type does not exist, depending on the type, Outlook may create and return the folder, or may raise an error.

para.span: 例如，如果 olFolderManagedEmail 指定为 FolderType，但是尚未部署托管文件夹组，Outlook 将引发错误。

span.span: For example, if olFolderManagedEmail is specified as the FolderType but the Managed Folders group has not been deployed, then Outlook raises an error.
